    <br>preferences or unsubscribe from this list. Follow us:
    <a href="https://twitter.com/crowdfrica?lang=en" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/crowdfrica/" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/crowdfrica/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
  </p>
  <p id="kati" style="text-align: center;">Need help? Contact Us.<br>
    Crowdfrica.org, Impact Hub Accra, F393/3, Otswe Street, Osu, Accra-Ghana.
  </p>

</div>
